#

Slow Cooker Pulled Pork

495 min
$15
400 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

Dairy-FreeGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasySlow CookerComfort Food

Description

Tender, juicy pulled pork that melts in your mouth, perfect for sandwiches or on its own!

Ingredients

  • pork shoulder: 3 pounds
  • barbecue sauce: 1 cup
  • chicken broth: 1 cup
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • apple cider vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • brown sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1 teaspoon
  • smoked paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
